{"serial": "36008", "department_serial": 35, "code": "EN6070", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Special Topics in Water Treatment", "ch": "水處理特論"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Lin, Po-Hsun"], "ch": ["林伯勳"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 5, "session": ["2", "3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "E3", "room": "207"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "環境工程研究所碩士班", "en": "MSc in Environmental Engineering"}, "system": {"ch": "碩博同修", "en": "Master/Doctoral Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "英語", "en": "English"}, "card": {"ch": "不使用", "en": "None"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 23, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本特論課程為授課教師歷年來在水處理及水回收方面所進行的研究，以及過去在業界的實務經驗介紹。課程內容包含基本的質能平衡、水質參數介紹、飲用水處理程序、廢水處理程序、氨氮處理、薄膜技術於水處理回收技術的應用、水與能源等。使學生除了可提升在水處理方面的研究能量，更能提升在實務上的應用能力，強化未來進入職場的競爭力。", "en": "The topics include research topics conducted by the instructor and his practical experiences in the industry. The content consists of material balances, an introduction to water quality parameters, drinking water treatment processes, wastewater treatment processes, ammonia nitrogen treatment, application of membrane technology in water treatment and reclamation, water and energy. The objective of this course is to enable students to inspire their research in water treatment and enhance their capability in practical."}, "outline": {"ch": "1.質量平衡及因次分析\n2.水質參數介紹\n3.飲用水處理程序\n4.消毒副產物\n5.廢水處理程序\n6.氨氮處理\n7.薄膜於水處理回收技術的應用 (各種薄膜種類、技術介紹，如MBR, MF、UF、NF、RO、FO、EDR、MD、CDI)\n8.水與能源", "en": "1.Material balance and dimensional analysis\n2.Water quality and bottled water\n3.Drinking water treatment\n4.Disinfection by-products\n5.Wastewater treatment\n6.Ammonia removal\n7.Application of membrane technology to water treatment and reclamation (ex, MBR, MF、UF、NF、RO、FO、EDR、MD、CDI)\n8.Water and energy"}, "textbook": {"ch": "“Metcalf ＆ Eddy, Wastewater Engineering - Treatment and Reuse (4th edition)\n自編教材“", "en": "“Metcalf ＆ Eddy, Waste